# Allowlist mode: ignore everything by default at the project root.
# Only the addon body and standard public-facing files are tracked.
# Everything else (reference/, docs/, tools/, .claude/, dist/, *.client etc.)
# stays local but never reaches GitHub.

# Default: ignore everything at the project root
/*

# Explicitly track these
!/.gitignore
!/README.md
!/CHANGELOG.md
!/LICENSE
!/camera_shift_sync/

# Safety-net patterns that apply inside tracked directories too
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/*$py.class
**/*.so
**/.Python
**/*.egg-info/
**/.eggs/
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/desktop.ini
**/*.blend1
**/*.blend2
**/*.blend@
